{"about_the_game":"<strong>Before playing The Unluckiest Man, check this amazing new project which I am working on!</strong><br>Explore spine-tingling psychologica horrors in my upcoming game as we journey into the 1940s.<br><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140900/extras/Gif2.gif?t=1719083307\" /><br><br>Immerse yourself in the dark tragic-comic adventure of &quot;The Unluckiest Man&quot;, a short free narrative experience with light puzzle elements.<br><br>Play as Dragomir, a widower who has just lost his beloved wife after a long suffering caused by tuberculosis. Following her death, Dragomir is struggling, having to prepare Catrina's funeral while being completely broke and with no one to help him.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140900/extras/Gif1.gif?t=1719083307\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Explore your dilapidated house as well as the rest of the fishing town in first person mode, while trying to make sense of the uncomfortable situation you find yourself in.<br></li><li> Find keys, collect various items and solve light puzzles to progress the story.<br></li><li> Notes are spread around, revealing more about your past and hinting at your future. <br></li><li> Talk to the townsfolk and see if they are willing to help you or at least show a bit of compassion.<br></li><li> Read the newspaper to delight in some of the city's most exciting gossip.<br></li><li> Set in Romania, the game features Romanian voice acting with English subtitles.<br></li><li> Check your inventory to see your collected items and read your found notes and newspaper articles.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140900/extras/TUM_Banner1.png?t=1719083307\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2140900/page_bg_generated_v6b.